<h1>training</h1>

<h3>professional development & skills for visual artists</h3>

<p>We take pride in offering excellent training in a range of relavent subjects, for visual artists around the North West.
But don't take our word for it, here are some comments from partipants on past courses:</p>

<p><i>“I found this workshop the most useful I have ever attended...the time just flew by.”</i></p>
<p><i>“This was a very useful, information dense workshop, filled with knowledge gained from experience and good suggestions of how to apply it.”</i></p>
<p><i>“Exceeded all expectations”</i></p>


