<ul>

<li><p><b>Build Your Own Website <i><br>LED BY – Matthew Thomas</i><br>
Tuesday evenings, 6.45-9.30pm, starts 16th April 2013.</b></p>
<p>Using free software, you will learn to design, build optimise and publish your own website. 
Suitable for complete beginners (no coding experience necessary), participants will need to bring a laptop.
</p>
<p><b>PRICE- £75 (5 sessions)</b></p> 
</li>


<li><p><b>Design Your Own Marketing Materials <i><br>LED BY – Matthew Thomas</i><br>
Tuesday evenings, 6.45-9.30pm, starts 21st May 2013.</b></p>
<p>Using free software, you will learn to design, and create your own Posters, Flyers, Letterheads, Business cards and more. 
Suitable for complete beginners, participants will need to bring a laptop.
</p>
<p><b>PRICE- £75 (5 sessions)</b></p>
